@startuml
title Healthcare Portal - User Login State Machine Diagram

state PortalChoice1 <<choice>>
state PortalChoice2 <<choice>>
state PortalChoice3 <<choice>>
state ServiceCenterRegistration <<choice>>
state OwnerJoin <<choice>>
state ServiceCenterVerification
state ServiceCenterLogin
state ServiceCenterHome
state Logout
state NewsContent
state HealthInfo
state PaymentSelection
state InsuranceCheck
state DoctorConsultationPayment
state DrugPurchasePayment
state FeedbackCollection

[*] --> PortalChoice1

PortalChoice1 --> PortalChoice2 : [Healthcare Portal]
PortalChoice1 --> PortalChoice3 : [Patient Portal]

PortalChoice2 --> ServiceCenterRegistration : [New User Registration]
PortalChoice2 --> ServiceJoin : [Registered User]
PortalChoice3 --> CarOwnerRegistration : [New Patient Registration]
PortalChoice3 --> OwnerJoin : [Registered Patient]

state "Service Center Registration" as ServiceCenterRegistration
ServiceCenterRegistration : entry / Unregistered user
ServiceCenterRegistration : do / Enter Valid Credentials
ServiceCenterRegistration : exit / Account registered

state "Service Center Verification" as ServiceCenterVerification
ServiceCenterVerification : entry / User account registered
ServiceCenterVerification : do / Verify User
ServiceCenterVerification : exit / Login Successful

state "Service Center Login" as ServiceCenterLogin
ServiceCenterLogin : entry / Verified User
ServiceCenterLogin : entry / User not logged in
ServiceCenterLogin : do / Authenticate User
ServiceCenterLogin : exit / Logged In Successfully

state "Service center Home" as ServiceCenterHome
ServiceCenterHome : entry / Logged in User
ServiceCenterHome : do / Display home page
ServiceCenterHome : exit / Read News and Expert Content
ServiceCenterHome : exit / Check Symptoms or Fitness
ServiceCenterHome : exit / Logout

state "Read News and Expert Content" as NewsContent
NewsContent : entry / To read news and expert content
NewsContent : do / Display news and expert content
NewsContent : exit / Return to Service center home page

state "Check Symptoms or Fitness" as HealthInfo
HealthInfo : entry / To check symptoms or fitness
HealthInfo : do / Check symptoms or fitness
HealthInfo : exit / Return to Service center home page

state "Logout" as Logout
Logout : entry / To Logout
Logout : do / Logout
Logout : exit / Logged out Successfully

ServiceCenterHome --> NewsContent : [Read News and Expert Content]
ServiceCenterHome --> HealthInfo : [Check Symptoms or Fitness]
NewsContent --> ServiceCenterHome : [Return to Service center home page]
HealthInfo --> ServiceCenterHome : [Return to Service center home page]
ServiceCenterHome --> Logout : [Logout]

state "Payment Selection" as PaymentSelection
PaymentSelection : entry / To select payment method
PaymentSelection : do / Display payment methods
PaymentSelection : exit / Select Cash or Insurance

state "Insurance Check" as InsuranceCheck
InsuranceCheck : entry / To check insurance for finance-related services
InsuranceCheck : do / Process and validate insurance
InsuranceCheck : exit / Insurance processed successfully

state "Doctor Consultation Payment" as DoctorConsultationPayment
DoctorConsultationPayment : entry / To pay for doctor consultation
DoctorConsultationPayment : do / Check payment with insurance and complete the process
DoctorConsultationPayment : exit / Payment completed successfully

state "Drug Purchase Payment" as DrugPurchasePayment
DrugPurchasePayment : entry / To pay for drug or supplement purchases
DrugPurchasePayment : do / Select payment method (cash or insurance)
DrugPurchasePayment : exit / Cash payment details provided if chosen as the payment method
DrugPurchasePayment --> InsuranceCheck : [Insurance-based payments]
InsuranceCheck --> DrugPurchasePayment : [Complete the payment process for insurance-based payments]

state "Feedback Collection" as FeedbackCollection
FeedbackCollection : entry / To collect user feedback after service completion
FeedbackCollection : do / Collect and store user feedback
FeedbackCollection : exit / Feedback collected successfully

ServiceCenterHome --> PaymentSelection : [Select payment method]
PaymentSelection --> InsuranceCheck : [Insurance check]
InsuranceCheck --> DrugPurchasePayment : [Drug or supplement purchases]
DrugPurchasePayment --> InsuranceCheck : [Insurance-based payments]
PaymentSelection --> DoctorConsultationPayment : [Doctor consultation
@enduml
